\pard\f0\fs28 Leaves alternate. Bracteoles 3. Perianth-segments 5, oblong, acute or obtuse. Stamens 5, alternating with 5 teeth; filaments connate below into a membranous tube. Style long, filiform. Fruit circumscissile; seeds numerous.
